{"tid":2080518,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"唔洗OT既國家 ，90後港女打工移民冰島享受無壓力生活","createTime":"2020-06-26T13:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T16:11:29.000Z","uid":353419,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"215845f7ce3048f2476bc44735f63e064c40f4d9","tid":2080518,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:01:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5WBMXB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5WBMXB.jpg&h=1eb30615&s={SIZE}\" /> 在英國倫敦畢業後，呀丹輾轉寄了一封求職信到冰島，面試成功，便正式搬到冰島工作生活<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ds29nwv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDs29nwv.jpg&h=907303b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呀丹既職業係冰島旅遊blogger。她表示，外國人係冰島難搵工，因為冰島公司請外國人好多支出，例如簽証交稅保險等等....<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UtrBMZO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUtrBMZO.jpg&h=b68b2fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但如果有冰島公司肯請你，生活會比香港輕鬆，每日工作8小時，冇OT，每年好多假，復活節都已有24日有薪假<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAku6YS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAku6YS.jpg&h=5f132db1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過冰島稅高，佔打工收入37%，相對地福利都好，例如患癌症有免費醫療<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bq0CwtC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbq0CwtC.jpg&h=1a24da81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呀丹表示冰島冇投資移民，方法得打工同結婚兩個，住夠4年就拎到永久居留權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMyXwu3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMyXwu3.jpg&h=fb402c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時呀丹月租$9,400港元，租住約800呎的公寓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nm7UyHc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnm7UyHc.jpg&h=030dd2a9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n市中心黃金地段獨立屋700至1000萬港元左右，2人居住公寓至少200至300萬港元。其他小鎮樓價相對平啲<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2100217/%E7%84%A1%E9%9C%80OT%E7%9A%84%E6%85%A2%E6%B4%BB%E5%9C%8B%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%8090%E5%BE%8C%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E7%A7%BB%E5%B1%85%E5%86%B0%E5%B3%B6%E4%BA%AB%E5%8F%97%E7%84%A1%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2100217%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%259C%2580OT%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2585%25A2%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E3%2580%258090%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%2586%25B0%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E5%258F%2597%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%258A%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h0ZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=b02d2e66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2100217/%E7%84%A1%E9%9C%80OT%E7%9A%84%E6%85%A2%E6%B4%BB%E5%9C%8B%E5%BA%A6%E3%80%8090%E5%BE%8C%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E7%A7%BB%E5%B1%85%E5%86%B0%E5%B3%B6%E4%BA%AB%E5%8F%97%E7%84%A1%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冰島生活節奏慢 ，對當地人黎講，「好快」姐係2日左右"},{"pid":"9b15c51c7454e181c665391e084c053897b4a57b","tid":2080518,"uid":201604,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:07:24.000Z","msg":"首先要有錢移民"},{"pid":"90a9e6166d688622b830089bb8d83610fb2df291","tid":2080518,"uid":353419,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9b15c51c7454e181c665391e084c053897b4a57b","tid":2080518,"uid":201604,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:07:24.000Z","msg":"首先要有錢移民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:07:42.000Z","msg":"冰島冇投資移民"},{"pid":"41cfb745da674ded804eda56f237a133e1b60dbe","tid":2080518,"uid":224882,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:10:32.000Z","msg":"淨係學冰島話呢下都已經好難"},{"pid":"7760a